I guess I'll just ask in here since Google is being surprisingly useless on this topic and I didn't have much success looking through the forum.

Are there any master threads for discussing parts the game seems like it should have, based on what it does have, but that it doesn't actually have? Parts that perhaps are frequently requested? I've ended up making a whole list but one example is a Size 2 nuclear engine. This "filling in the gaps" seems like a topic on which the modding community would be jumping all the time, as filling said gaps with mods would require downloading multiple mods from different developers that are all but guaranteed to add a bunch of extra parts, which isn't bad per se but alters the game beyond the scope of simply filling gaps. I think I'm rambling here xP

I ask here because I don't want to create a redundant new thread just to discover that there are already 99 other threads tackling the same concept and I was just blind... or that this is a forbidden topic and I didn't see the rule about it because, again, I was blind ^^;
